      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个RAG系统的完整架构图。核心是把知识库、检索流程和生成流程串起来。先有个整体框架：左边是知识库准备，中间是向量数据库，右边是用户查询和模型响应。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Knowledge_Base",
        "Vector_Database",
        "User_Query",
        "Language_Model"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。知识库部分需要展开吗？比如文档是怎么处理的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Knowledge_Base"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "要的。知识库内部有两个关键节点：原始的文档集合，还有切分后的文档块。文档集合经过切分处理变成文档块，这是第一步1a。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Document_Collection",
        "Document_Chunks"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我在知识库子图里放了Document_Collection和Document_Chunks，用1a标注了切分处理的关系。接下来知识库和向量数据库怎么连？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Knowledge_Base",
        "Document_Collection",
        "Document_Chunks",
        "Vector_Database"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "文档块生成嵌入向量，存到向量数据库。这是步骤1b，标注为Generate Embeddings。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Knowledge_Base",
        "Document_Chunks",
        "Vector_Database"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "1b的关系加好了。现在看查询侧，用户查询进来之后怎么处理？",
