      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "用户查询先变成查询嵌入，步骤2a。然后查询嵌入去向量数据库做相似度搜索，步骤2b。这两个节点需要明确标出来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User_Query",
        "Query_Embedding",
        "Vector_Database"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Query_Embedding节点，2a和2b的关系也连上了。搜索之后返回什么？",
